@startuml
!theme plain
title Назначение курса группе + прогресс студента

actor "Преподаватель" as Teacher
actor "Студент" as Student
participant "CourseController" as CourseCtrl
participant "CourseService" as CourseSvc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Преподаватель назначает курс группе ==

Teacher -> CourseCtrl: POST /api/courses/{courseId}/groups\n{ groupIds: [...] }
CourseCtrl -> CourseSvc: AssignGroupsAsync(courseId, req, ct)
CourseSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses WHERE id = @courseId
DB --> CourseSvc: Course
CourseSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO course_groups\n{ course_id, group_id } (for each group)
DB --> CourseSvc: ok
CourseSvc --> CourseCtrl: Result.Ok()
CourseCtrl --> Teacher: 200 OK

== Студент видит свой прогресс ==

Student -> CourseCtrl: GET /api/my/courses/{id}/progress
CourseCtrl -> CourseSvc: GetProgressAsync(courseId, studentId, ct)
CourseSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM assignments\nWHERE course_id = @courseId
DB --> CourseSvc: List<Assignment>
CourseSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM assignment_submissions\nWHERE student_id = @studentId\nAND assignment_id IN (...)
DB --> CourseSvc: List<Submission>
CourseSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM tests WHERE course_id = @courseId
DB --> CourseSvc: List<Test>
CourseSvc -> DB: SELECT * FROM test_attempts\nWHERE student_id = @studentId AND test_id IN (...)
DB --> CourseSvc: List<TestAttempt>
CourseSvc -> CourseSvc: Calculate: completed/total, average score
CourseSvc --> CourseCtrl: Result.Ok({ completionPercent, assignmentsProgress, testsProgress, averageScore })
CourseCtrl --> Student: 200 JSON
@enduml
